		<table width="100%">
		<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    1hslash vs 2hslash guide</b></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><A href="mailto:pestalince@hotmail.com">Ragnarokk</a> | 
		            11/10/1999 6:35:16 PM</b></font></p>
		         <a href="guides.asp">
		         <font face="verdana" size="2">Return to guide listing.</font></a>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">On the subject of 1hVS2h. I have a very lean ogre warrior with 150Str. I think the better your Str, the faster your weapon should be. If you notice, most the of the fast 1hs (Tent wip, barbed L wip, Lseax, bladed claws) are in the hands of Ogres, trolls, barbs, and dwarves. When was the last time you saw a High elf paladin or Wood Elf ranger with a tent wip? As a level 14 ogre warrior, I use my Barbed leather wip, and Shield of the Slain Unicorn. I have an Executioners axe, but the 31 damage cap and the fact that I  can't use the haste hurts me, so I don't use it unless its to max out my skill. I like to use the Wip, because in never hit for less than max damage with my wip (14-16) I am sure the 1hVS2h all depends on race(str). As you look above, most of the people that like 2h are Elves, humans, and other small races. As an ogre, I like 1h. Why? I like the speed, and the 9ac and 20 or so damage from my Shield of the slain unicorn. If you say my shield attacks half as offen as my wip, and you factor the 40 delay, the shield attacks once per 3 attacks of the wip. Thats about 23 damage in 1 round, next to my Executioners axes 31. The Axe has a delay of 50(without haste, mind you). The wip is about 40% faster, so i would say at my level, 1h is better. I also get 9AC from my Shield of the Slain Unicorn.<BR>
<BR>
I rarely miss, (89Dex), and always hit for max damage. Add full bronze, and im a wrecking ball. A wallking fort. Jumbo 50% larger can of woopass. Maybe when i get to level 20, the damage cap will be lifted, my axe will be able to use its haste efect. For now im going to stick with the wip and shield. I hope this helped you people. <BR>
<BR>
Ragnarokk, 14th level ogre warrior, Fennin Ro
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
